e of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GLOBAL_SKILL_GROUP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SKILL_SUBTITLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Global Hero Skill</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ogólna umiejętność bohatera</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill tree header.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VITALITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vitality 1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żywotność 1</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VITALITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vitality 2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żywotność 2</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VITALITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vitality 3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żywotność 3</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VITALITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero gains {VitalityBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater zyskuje {VitalityBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CLOSE_QUARTERS_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Close Quarters Specialist 1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki w zwarciu 1</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CLOSE_QUARTERS_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Close Quarters Specialist 2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki w zwarciu 2</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CLOSE_QUARTERS_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Close Quarters Specialist 3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki w zwarciu 3</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CLOSE_QUARTERS_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Increases damage dealt with melee weapons by {CloseBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwiększa obrażenia zadawane bronią do walki wręcz o {CloseBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STANDARD_MODIFIERS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EXTRA_DAMAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero's inspiring leadership gives this unit {DamageBonus} extra damage.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zdolności przywódcze bohatera zapewniają tej jednostce {DamageBonus} dodatkowych obrażeń.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANGED_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ranged Specialist 1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki dystansowej 1</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANGED_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ranged Specialist 2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki dystansowej 2</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANGED_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ranged Specialist 3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Specjalista od walki dystansowej 3</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RANGED_SPECIALIST</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Increases damage dealt with ranged weapons by {RangedBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwiększa obrażenia zadawane bronią dystansową o {RangedBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEAD_EYE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dead Eye 1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelec wyborowy 1</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEAD_EYE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dead Eye 2</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelec wyborowy 2</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEAD_EYE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dead Eye 3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelec wyborowy 3</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name. The numbers indicate the strength of the skill and should be retained.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEAD_EYE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">All attacks gain {DeadEyeBonus} more accuracy and critical hit chance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki zyskują {DeadEyeBonus} do celności i do szansy na trafienie krytyczne.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEAD_EYE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{DeadEyeBonus} extra accuracy and critical hit chance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{DeadEyeBonus} do celności i do szansy na trafienie krytyczne.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PILOTING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Piloting</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pilot</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PILOTING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero can now equip Tier I and II vehicles.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater może korzystać z pojazdów I i II klasy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ADVANCED_PILOTING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Piloting (Advanced)</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pilot (zaawansowany)</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ADVANCED_PILOTING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero can now equip Tier III vehicles.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater może korzystać z pojazdów III klasy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AIR_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Air Commander</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dowódca sił powietrznych</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AIR_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">All Flying units in the hero's army deal {commanderBonus} additional damage.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wszystkie jednostki latające w armii bohatera zadają obrażenia zwiększone o {commanderBonus}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Commander in this case means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROUND_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ground Commander</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dowódca sił pancernych</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROUND_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">All Heavy Ground units in the hero's army deal {commanderBonus} additional damage.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wszystkie ciężkie jednostki lądowe w armii bohatera zadają obrażenia zwiększone o {commanderBonus}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Commander in this case means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INFANTRY_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Infantry Commander</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dowódca piechoty</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INFANTRY_COMMANDER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">All Light Ground units in the hero's army deal {commanderBonus} additonal damage.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wszystkie lekkie jednostki lądowe w armii bohatera zadają obrażenia zwiększone o {commanderBonus}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Commander in this case means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PRIMARY_MODULAR_EXPANSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Modular Extension</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rozwinięcie modułowe</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PRIMARY_MODULAR_EXPANSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Allows the hero to equip an extra Mod.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pozwala bohaterowi używać dodatkowego modułu.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Mods are items that can be attached to units, normally up to 3. This skill allows 4 mods to be carried</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WATCHMAN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Watchman</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strażnik</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WATCHMAN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero gains Overwatch on all primary ranged attacks, and has an increased {watchmanBonus} accuracy with Overwatch attacks.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater zyskuje wartę w przypadku wszystkich głównych ataków dystansowych. Ataki warty mają celność zwiększoną o {watchmanBonus}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Overwatch is an ability that modifies existing attacks.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STEADY_AIM</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Steady Aim</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Celowanie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STEADY_AIM</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Attacks with ranged weapons are {steadyAimBonus} more accurate when fired from cover.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki bronią dystansową spod osłony mają dodatkowo {steadyAimBonus} celności.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">STEADY_AIM</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{steadyAimBonus} extra accuracy when firing from cover.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{steadyAimBonus} do celności w przypadku ataku spod osłony.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">COUNTER_ATTACK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Counter Attack</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kontratak</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">COUNTER_ATTACK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Melee Overwatch can no longer be cancelled by Stagger, and will never miss.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tryb warty w walce wręcz już nie chybia i nie można go przerwać zachwianiem.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALL_ROUND_AWARENESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">All-round Awareness</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nieustanna czujność</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALL_ROUND_AWARENESS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero can no longer be flanked.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohatera nie można już oskrzydlać.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TIRELESS_FIGHTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Martial Artist: Tireless</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sztuki walki – nieustępliwość</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TIRELESS_FIGHTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero gains Tireless, allowing it to trigger Melee Overwatch multiple times in a turn (though never twice against the same target).</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater zyskuje nieustępliwość, co umożliwia aktywowanie walki wręcz w trybie warty wielokrotnie w jednej turze (ale nigdy powtórnie wobec tego samego celu).</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FIRST_STRIKE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Martial Artist: First Strike</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sztuki walki – pierwsze uderzenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FIRST_STRIKE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero gains First Strike, meaning its Melee Overwatch triggers before the target that triggers it acts, unless the unit is Flanked.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater zyskuje pierwsze uderzenie, co oznacza, że jego atak wręcz w trybie warty następuje przed atakiem wroga, chyba że bohater jest oskrzydlony.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PERSONAL_WEAPON_EXPERT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Personal Weapons Expert</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Osobisty ekspert od uzbrojenia</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PERSONAL_WEAPON_EXPERT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When not in a vehicle, the hero's attacks gain {DamageBonus} damage and {AccuracyBonus} accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy bohater nie korzysta z pojazdu, jego ataki zyskują {DamageBonus} do obrażeń i {AccuracyBonus} do celności.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PERSONAL_DEFENSE_EXPERT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Personal Defense Expert</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Osobisty ekspert od obrony</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PERSONAL_DEFENSE_EXPERT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When not in a vehicle, the hero gains {ShieldBonus} shields and {ArmorBonus} armor.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy bohater nie korzysta z pojazdu, zyskuje {ShieldBonus} do tarcz i {ArmorBonus} do pancerza.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">A type of hero skill used by Oathbound heroes to give bonuses to colonies</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OATHBOUND_COLONY_SKILL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SKILL_SUBTITLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Oathbound Colony Skill</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umiejętność kolonialna Nieugiętych</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Text between {} should NOT be localized as they are numerical values in-game. Text between [] should NOT be localized as they are either icons or text formatting

EXAMPLE: "Hero gains {PersonaAccDmg} increased damage and accuracy " looks in-game like "Hero gains +5 increased damage and accuracy"</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><Panes><Pane><Number>3</Number><ActiveRow>4</ActiveRow><ActiveCol>10</ActiveCol></Pane></Panes><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>